title: Xbox 360 CON Resigner
description:
Name: Xbox 360 CON Resigner
Description: Resigns Xbox 360 CON files.
Author: Unknown
Released: 5-11-2008

If you receive the error "Component &#039;MSWINSCK.OCX&#039; or one of its dependencies not correctly registered: a file is missing or invalid," you must install MSWINSCK.OCX, as it is required to run Xbox 360 CON Resigner. To install MSWINSCK.OCX, goto http://www.ascentive.com/support/new/support_dll.phtml?dllname=MSWINSCK.OCX . Enjoy!
